## 1. Monolithic Architecture

All application components (UI, business logic, database access) are packaged and deployed as a **single unit**.

```
+------------------------------------+
|          MONOLITHIC APP            |
|  +--------+  +--------+  +------+ |
|  |   UI   |  | Logic  |  | Data | |
|  +--------+  +--------+  +------+ |
+------------------------------------+
                  |
             +----v----+
             |   DB    |
             +---------+
```

| Property | Value |
|---|---|
| Deployment | Single unit |
| Scalability | Vertical |
| Coupling | High |
| Complexity | Low |

**When to use:** Small teams, early-stage startups, simple applications, rapid prototyping.

