## 8. Clean Architecture

By **Robert C. Martin (Uncle Bob)**. Code organized in concentric circles — inner circles know nothing about outer circles. Dependency always points inward.

```
+----------------------------------------+
|       FRAMEWORKS & DRIVERS (outer)     |
|   +--------------------------------+   |
|   |     INTERFACE ADAPTERS         |   |
|   |   +------------------------+   |   |
|   |   |        USE CASES       |   |   |
|   |   |   +----------------+   |   |   |
|   |   |   |    ENTITIES    |   |   |   |
|   |   |   +----------------+   |   |   |
|   |   +------------------------+   |   |
|   +--------------------------------+   |
+----------------------------------------+
```

**When to use:** Long-lived software, domain-heavy systems, high testability requirements.

