## 10. CQRS + Event Sourcing

**CQRS:** Separate models for reading and writing.
**Event Sourcing:** Instead of storing current state, store a sequence of events.

```
           WRITE SIDE          READ SIDE

  User --> Command --> Handler --> Event Store
                                       |
                                  +----v------+
                                  | Projection|
                                  | Read Model|
                                  +-----+-----+
                                        |
                                  User <-+
```

**When to use:** Finance, audit systems, collaborative apps, systems requiring history replay.

