## 11. Pipe and Filter Architecture

Data flows through **processing steps (filters)** connected by channels (pipes). Each filter transforms data independently.

```
Input --> [Filter A] --> [Filter B] --> [Filter C] --> Output
          (Validate)    (Transform)      (Enrich)
```

**When to use:** ETL pipelines, compilers, data transformation, Unix shell pipes, Apache Camel.

