## Architecture Decision Map

### By Team Scale

| Team Size | Recommended Architecture |
|---|---|
| Small (1–5 devs) | Monolithic, Layered, Clean Architecture |
| Medium (5–20 devs) | Modular Monolith, SOA |
| Large (20–100 devs) | Microservices, EDA, DDD |
| Massive (100+ devs) | Cell-Based, Data Mesh |

### By Domain

| Domain | Recommended Architecture |
|---|---|
| E-Commerce | Microservices, SAGA, BFF |
| Analytics / BI | Lambda, Kappa, Data Mesh |
| Real-time / IoT | EDA, Edge, Reactive, Actor Model |
| Financial / Banking | CQRS, DDD, SOA |

### By Key Concern

| Concern | Architecture |
|---|---|
| Fault Tolerance | Cell-Based, Reactive |
| Auditability | Event Sourcing, CQRS |
| Scalability | Serverless, Space-Based, Shared-Nothing |
| Team Autonomy | Microservices, Microfrontend |

### AI Generation Hints

| User says... | Suggest... |
|---|---|
| startup, fast MVP | Monolithic |
| many teams, independent deploys | Microservices |
| real-time, events, notifications | EDA, Reactive |
| audit, history, undo | CQRS + Event Sourcing |
| massive data, analytics | Lambda / Kappa / Data Mesh |
| IoT, edge, low latency | Edge Computing |
| plugin system, marketplace | Plugin Architecture |
| migrate legacy | Strangler Fig |
| mobile + web + TV | BFF |
| blockchain, decentralized | P2P |

